We are Points

We’re a technology company working in the loyalty e-commerce industry. Our solutions enhance the management and monetization of loyalty currencies for more than 50 of the world’s largest loyalty brands, from frequent flyer miles and hotel points to retailer and credit card rewards. Supported by our unparalleled loyalty industry experience and technological expertise, we bring state-of-the-art loyalty commerce platforms and products to individuals and businesses in today’s loyalty marketplace.
					



Our Gateway to the Loyalty Ecosystem

						A single integration into our loyalty commerce platform opens up a wealth of opportunities to attract new members, increase engagement and boost ancillary revenue. Browse some of our solutions below.
					





									Points Loyalty Wallet
								

									The wallet connects loyalty programs, digital wallets, apps and retailers to their members and customers by seamlessly integrating loyalty into everyday transactions.
								


								learn more
								







									Points Travel
								

									The first private label travel e-commerce platform designed for the loyalty industry, Points Travel lets users earn and spend miles on travel bookings.
								


								learn more
								









									Buy, Gift & Transfer
								

									By enabling members to buy, gift and transfer their loyalty currency, our loyalty program partners generate millions in ancillary revenue and increase member engagement.
								


								learn more
								







									Points Business Solutions
								

									Points Business Solutions enables businesses to drive behavior and reward their customers with points and miles from the world's largest loyalty programs.
								


								learn more
								





See all of our solutions




The Points Loyalty Network

						Our network of loyalty program partners reaches across industries and around the globe.
					




















































See all of our partners







      About Points      

Points, publicly traded as Points International Ltd. (TSX:PTS) (NASDAQ:PCOM), is the global leader in loyalty currency management. Via a state-of-the-art loyalty commerce platform, Points provides loyalty eCommerce and technology solutions to the world's top brands to enhance their consumer offerings and streamline their back-end operations.



          learn more about points          













Points Business Solutions | Points
























































						Points Business Solutions
					

						Buy points and miles from loyalty giants to award to your customers
					








						Points Business Solutions enable any business to incentivize and reward its customers with loyalty points or miles from the world’s most popular loyalty brands. Getting started is quick, painless, and best of all, it generates real value by incentivizing customers to develop deeper relationships with your business.
					






						How it Works
					




									PointsConnect
								

									Businesses purchase points/miles from the loyalty program of their choice, and award them to customers as incentives.
								





									PointsSelect
								

									Businesses award customers with a set amount of points/miles, and the customer then selects the loyalty program with which they want to earn their reward.
								




						Points Business Solutions require little IT integration. Onboarding either PointsConnect or PointsSelect can happen in as little as a few weeks. You’ll also benefit from the full marketing and strategic support from our team of loyalty experts.
					



Benefits
Attract new customers

						Align your business with globally established loyalty programs and benefit from their 400+ million members' desire to earn more rewards.
					
Boost engagement

						Gain greater category share by incenting and rewarding your existing customers with the loyalty currencies they’re already passionate about.
					
Maximize revenue per basket

						Awarding currency from established loyalty programs has been proven to affect consumers’ purchasing decisions, from what they buy to how much.
					






