Our Culture | Points






























































				    Our Culture
				    
				      Living our motto: More together.
				    






Our Culture and Values

						At Points, we focus on results – we do what we have to do to get the job done and have fun doing it.
						

We act with INTEGRITY – we do the right thing, always.
We champion INNOVATION – we respectfully challenge the status quo.
We bring PASSION to our work – we have pride in what we do and how we do it.
We promote a CARING culture – we do great things with cool people.
We foster COLLABORATION with all our partners – we know that we are more together.


