Points International is a Canadian marketing company.  It specializes in providing reward and loyalty currency programs to businesses.
Points International is a Canadian marketing company.  It specializes in providing reward and loyalty currency programs to businesses.

The IT department of Points International consists of teams for database administration, application development, and systems administration.  Internal IT is within the domain… MorePoints International is a Canadian marketing company.  It specializes in providing reward and loyalty currency programs to businesses.

The IT department of Points International consists of teams for database administration, application development, and systems administration.  Internal IT is within the domain of the company's Chief Technology Officer who also oversees product-side technology operations and strategy for the company.

The company's servers run on Windows Server systems and are virtualized using VMware.  Points' applications environment revolves around Microsoft and Oracle technologies.





